HEADWORD: Huchen
<hw>Hu"chen</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A large salmon (<spn>Salmo hucho</spn> <it>or</it> <spn>Salvelinus
hucho</spn>) inhabiting the Danube; -- called also
<altname>huso</altname>, and <altname>bull trout</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

